target_raw:
I shall receive 4 talents 28 minas copper to be secured in the colony office in Burušḫattum.
I have deposited 1
the 20 minas of copper, my transport tariff, Iddin-Ištar will claim from the colony;
Iddin-Ištar will receive 20 minas when the copper comes out;
38 minas of copper Kuzallum will receive;
the rest of my copper amounts to 3 1/2 talents.
Thereof Aššur-ṭāb will receive 3 talents 10 minas, my fees.
7 kutānu-textiles and 4 minas 2 shekels of silver I left for Iddin-Ištar.

